{"tid":1026314,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"拜祖先墳墓垮掉…壓中孝子孝孫釀1死","createTime":"2019-02-18T04:23:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T08:59:37.000Z","uid":34409,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"8384d19a40ec5433c1b741767382212a70f66d86","tid":1026314,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T04:23:22.000Z","msg":"大陸重慶一名姚性男子帶著妻子、女婿、孫子祭拜剛過世的岳父，沒想到拜到一半意外發生了！才剛立好10多天的墓碑突然塌下，近千斤重的石塊直接壓中孝子孝孫，釀成1死3傷。<br />\n<br />\n綜合陸媒報導，姚男過年期間帶著一家4口前往岳父墳前祭拜，他與女婿將鞭炮放好後，準備等妻子和孫子燒紙錢，不料才立了10多天的石墓碑，突然連同柱子垮下來，妻子、女婿與孫子慘被石頭壓住。<br />\n<br />\n附近民眾見狀後，趕緊協助送醫，不幸的是，姚男的老婆因傷勢過重，搶救無效死亡。據了解，姚男花了5800元人民幣（約新台幣2.64萬）立碑造墳，結果竟是豆腐渣工程，才完工10多天就垮掉。目前當地村委會、鎮政府已介入調查。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Ls4IquBHjD_iTXvdUF3uFA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9Mjg3/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/setn_com_683/9785cc0cb78855cdbafa395401169b8e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FLs4IquBHjD_iTXvdUF3uFA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9Mjg3%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fsetn_com_683%2F9785cc0cb78855cdbafa395401169b8e&h=d1114b63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%8B%9C%E7%A5%96%E5%85%88%E5%A2%B3%E5%A2%93%E5%9E%AE%E6%8E%89-%E5%A3%93%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%9D%E5%AD%90%E5%AD%9D%E5%AD%AB%E9%87%801%E6%AD%BB-005540342.html?fbclid=IwAR2EMhe0SSud-a6nZ781CI8xMkemQnocl7y4AKz8pYGxgfvupxOMZx3pxFU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%258B%259C%25E7%25A5%2596%25E5%2585%2588%25E5%25A2%25B3%25E5%25A2%2593%25E5%259E%25AE%25E6%258E%2589-%25E5%25A3%2593%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25AD%259D%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%25AD%259D%25E5%25AD%25AB%25E9%2587%25801%25E6%25AD%25BB-005540342.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2EMhe0SSud-a6nZ781CI8xMkemQnocl7y4AKz8pYGxgfvupxOMZx3pxFU&d=8lKb2kYWDOzPE5G8cc2TgP1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=5b491f25\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%8B%9C%E7%A5